          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Starting with a High Mobility Zaku -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On the second half of the first mission, there are two Musai cruisers carrying a Zaku II F and two Zaku Is each. Choose one Musai and ''sacrifice'' Saberfish fighters and Salamis cruisers to the Zaku II F. Once it hits ACE level, destroy the Musai while the Zaku II is deployed and capture it. On the next intermission, you can upgrade to a High Mobility Zaku immediately.</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
